# Place your AirVPN WireGuard .conf files here
# 
# Expected naming convention:
# AirVPN_AT-Vienna_Alderamin_UDP-1637-Entry3.conf
#
# The filename is parsed to extract:
# - Country code (AT)
# - City (Vienna)
# - Server name (Alderamin)
# - Protocol (UDP)
# - Port (1637)
# - Entry number (3)
#
# US servers are filtered to only include East Coast/Midwest locations
# (closer to Europe): New York, Chicago, Dallas, Atlanta, Washington DC

